00:56:49.329 --> 00:56:53.265
«Oh, Canada»

924
00:57:02.676 --> 00:57:07.409
"Jack Taylor. Rectacid.
Aplicar livremente nas nádegas,"


925
00:57:07.481 --> 00:57:12.043
